Interface RowDecoratorIterator

All Known Implementing Classes:
RowIteratorRowDecoratorIterator
public interface RowDecoratorIterator

A bidirectional iterator over a collection of RowDecorators. (Once current, next, previous, first, or last is invoked, all previously returned values are invalidated.)
